Software Engineering Methods Project

The Facebook

Corey Nagel, Matt Binsfeld, and Jordan Tsiao




Models:
Static_pages -
  mainpage/login page
  newsfeed- shows posts by users friends
  search for friends

Session - we need a session model to track when a user is logged in, dont generate this yet.

Users -
  profile page
  preferences page
  Create account

  has a wall
  has many relationships and microposts and comments
  attributes:
    first name
    last name
    Location
    School/Work
    bithdate
    interests
    quotes

Wall-
  belongs to user
  has many microposts

Relationship -
  connects users to other users via friend status

Micropost -
  belongs to user and a wall
  has many comments
  can only be seen by user's friends
  attributes:
    text

comment -
  belong to microposts and user
  attribute:
    text